OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,FScottish Labour has pledged to tackle
OL,8,F"gross inequalities" in cancer
OL,9,Fscreening, improve access and prevent
OL,10,Flong waits for treatment as part of
OL,11,Ftheir plan to deliver Scotland's
OL,12,Flifesaving waiting times standard.
OL,14,FThe party says the 62-day waiting
OL,15,Ftimes standard has not been met since
OL,16,F2012.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
