PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,FThey said if they win the Scottish
OL,8,Felections in May, they would roll out
OL,9,Fa modern screening programme for lung
OL,10,Fcancer, alongside a national programme
OL,11,Fof self-sampling for cervical cancer
OL,12,Fand a targeted prostate cancer
OL,13,Fscreening pilot.
OL,15,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,16,Fsaid: "People diagnosed with cancer,
OL,17,Fas well as their families, will
OL,18,Funderstandably feel great anxiety
OL,19,Fabout their treatment, which is only
OL,20,Fworsened by any delays they are then
OL,21,Ffaced with.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,F"There are still gross inequalities
OL,8,Fwhen it comes to screening and early
OL,9,Fdetection, all while lifesaving
OL,10,Ftreatment standards haven't been met
OL,11,Fin more than a decade.
OL,13,F"That is why Scottish Labour is
OL,14,Fcommitted to redoubling efforts to
OL,15,Fdetect cancer earlier, meet the
OL,16,Flifesaving 62-day cancer treatment
OL,17,Fstandard, and help give Scots the best
OL,18,Fchances of survival."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,FThe party have pledged that cancer
OL,8,Fpatients will be supported from
OL,9,Fsuspicion of cancer through their
OL,10,Ftreatment with a care navigator who
OL,11,Fwill ensure tests and results are
OL,12,Fdelivered on time.
OL,14,FPatients would also receive a tailored
OL,15,Fcare plan at diagnosis, covering
OL,16,Ftreatment, mental health support and
OL,17,Femployment guidance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,FMr Sarwar continued: "The truth is
OL,8,Fthat while the risk of dying from
OL,9,Fcancer in Scotland has decreased,
OL,10,Fuptake in screening programmes is
OL,11,Fstill below target, especially in
OL,12,Fcommunities that are hardest to reach.
OL,14,F"Hospitals are still using decades-old
OL,15,Fdiagnostics scanners, while the
OL,16,Fradiology workforce is burnt out and
OL,17,Fstretched to breaking point.
OL,19,F"We can't afford to let this situation
OL,20,Fcontinue, and for lifesaving treatment
OL,21,Ftargets to continue being missed."
OL,26,@oD@VOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,FScottish Labour health spokesperson
OL,8,FJackie Baillie said: "As part of our
OL,9,Fcommitment to improving the uptake of
OL,10,Fcancer screenings, we will work with
OL,11,Flocal community groups and trusted
OL,12,Fvoices who are friends and neighbours
OL,13,Fwho can help encourage people to
OL,14,Fattend an appointment.
OL,26,@pD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,F"And while the SNP government has been
OL,8,Fasleep at the wheel on lung cancer
OL,9,Fscreenings ` trailing behind England
OL,10,Fand Wales, who have set out a
OL,11,Ftimetable for national, targeted
OL,12,Fscreening programmes ` Scottish Labour
OL,13,Fwill do everything in our power to
OL,14,Fexpedite that process here.
OL,16,F"Under a Scottish Labour government,
OL,17,Fevery cancer patient will be
OL,18,Fguaranteed a named care navigator who
OL,19,Fwill support them and their family
OL,20,Fthrough their journey, from suspicion
OL,21,Fof cancer through to treatment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,F"The people of Scotland deserve better
OL,8,Fthan the SNP. They are out of ideas,
OL,9,Fout of energy, and out of time. In
OL,10,Fjust two months, the people of
OL,11,FScotland will be able to turn the page
OL,12,Fon 19 years of dismal SNP government
OL,13,Fand choose a new direction with Anas
OL,14,FSarwar and Scottish Labour."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
