CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,FThe commitment follows the
OL,8,Fannouncement from the party that it
OL,9,Fwill upgrade hospital scanners over a
OL,10,Fdecade old with new AI-enabled
OL,11,Fscanners that are faster, more
OL,12,Faccurate and increase the number of
OL,13,Fappointments available.
OL,15,FThis technology will help diagnose
OL,16,Fdegenerative diseases such as dementia
OL,17,Fand multiple sclerosis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,FPublic health minister Jenni Minto
OL,8,Fsaid: "The fact is that we are
OL,9,Ftreating more patients with cancer on
OL,10,Ftime, within both standards, compared
OL,11,Fto pre-pandemic. 95.1% of patients are
OL,12,Fbeing treated within 31 days of a
OL,13,Fdecision to treat, with the median
OL,14,Fwait for treatment just two days ` the
OL,15,Fjoint lowest on record.
OL,17,F"Diagnostic activity is up, meaning
OL,18,Fthousands more people getting their
OL,19,FMRIs and scans more quickly with
OL,20,Finvestigations for cancer prioritised
OL,21,Fwithin this.
OL,26,@pD@GOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,F"To improve cervical cancer detection,
OL,8,Fwe are already due to offer the first
OL,9,Fself-sampling kits this spring and we
OL,10,Fwill shortly publish our new cervical
OL,11,Fscreening action plan.
OL,13,F"The risk of dying from cancer in
OL,14,FScotland is now at the lowest rate on
OL,15,Frecord for both men and women, falling
OL,16,Fby 12.1% from 2015 to 2024. This
OL,17,Fencouraging trend reflects earlier
OL,18,Fdetection, more effective treatments
OL,19,Fand our continued investment in cancer
OL,20,Fservices.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773799382
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge to tackle
OL,4,C'gross inequalities' in cancer
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,F"We know there is still more to do but
OL,8,Fthese latest figures show that our
OL,9,Fplan is working and our NHS is turning
OL,10,Fa corner."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@JO]
